		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Everything in Battletoads:
<br />
<br />-whoever dies takes <em>both</em> players back to the last checkpoint
<br />-lack of time to decipher what the hell is going to happen in the next part of the level, resulting in a trial &amp; error game
<br />-one-hit kills
<br />-sudden incline in difficulty (Turbo Tunnel)
<br />-terrible controls
<br />-terrible physics (The Revolution) which is also guilty of the "platform is off the bottom of the screen, so you die" programming
<br />-12 freakin stages that had to be beaten in one sitting (warps do help, though)
<br />
<br />Yeah, this game sucks
<br />
